<%# `@comments` is set by show actions; new/edit pages don't, so
    fall back to a fresh fetch off the target so the panel can still
    list existing comments alongside the new-comment form. %>
<%= render(Views::Controllers::Comments::CommentsForObject.new(
             object: object,
             comments: @comments || Comment.where(target: object).to_a,
             user: @user, editable: false, limit: 10
           )) %>
